Package: mender-orchestrator-core
Architecture: any
Depends: mender-auth, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: mender-client
Description: Mender Orchestrator Core
 Mender Orchestrator orchestrates updates across multiple Components in a
 System, to ensure software consistency across the System as a whole. This
 package contains the core binary for standalone use cases.

Package: mender-orchestrator
Architecture: any
Depends: mender-orchestrator-core (= ${source:Version})
Recommends: mender-orchestrator-support
Description: Mender Orchestrator
 Mender Orchestrator orchestrates updates across multiple Components in a
 System, to ensure software consistency across the System as a whole. This
 meta-package installs the core binary and the support files for the most
 common use cases working together with the Mender Client.
